{
  "title": "Warm Crunchy Polish Mushroom Wrap",
  "description": "A salty and crunchy Polish dish featuring shoyu-koji and wrapped in a corn husk, perfect for a midnight craving. This ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly wrap is made with ssam-wrap inspired filling.",
  "cuisine": "Polish",
